{"tid":1550261,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好死","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T15:18:26.000Z","uid":227172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"625a9789a2dc225aef4bffe98019143bd81544c8","tid":1550261,"uid":227172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:18:01.000Z","msg":"呢一刻你覺得完全絕望<br />\n除咗死你睇唔倒其他出路<br />\n但係請你相信我<br />\n呢個世界絕對比你依家知道嘅大，可能性比你依家知道嘅多<br />\n俾一個機會自己試一試其他嘅可能先再諗死<br />\n如果呢一刻你覺得好辛苦，行唔倒落去<br />\n搵人幫你<br />\n唔好諗住靠自己<br />\n每個人都有需要人幫嘅時候<br />\n搵人幫你<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tm8LGxTLtQk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTm8LGxTLtQk&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=7d38534e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tm8LGxTLtQk</a><br />\nwell I do. I do care."},{"pid":"a988d8628d99c56999672b25fd84f1ec2537a097","tid":1550261,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:18:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}